# chktex configuration for TAOCP solutions
#
# Warning reference (https://www.nongnu.org/chktex/ChkTeX.pdf):
#   1  Command terminated with space
#   2  Non-breaking space (~) should have been used before reference
#   3  Enclose previous parenthesis with {}
#   8  Wrong length of dash (may be "-" vs "--" vs "---")
#   9  ) expected, found ...
#  10  Solo ) found
#  12  Interword spacing (\ ) after abbreviation period
#  13  Intersentence spacing (\@) before punctuation
#  15  No match for ( — cannot be suppressed inline
#  16  Mathmode still on at end of document
#  17  Number of ( doesn't match number of )
#  25  You might wish to put single-char subscripts in {}
#  27  Could not execute LaTeX command
#  35  You should use \gcd, \min, \max, etc.
#  36  You should put a space in front of parenthesis
#
# Warning 15 is globally suppressed because it cannot be suppressed inline.
# Warning 16 only appears in batch mode (multi-file) due to template resolution
# and is suppressed to allow batch validation.
#
# IMPORTANT: Run chktex from each file's directory (or use the provided script)
# so that \input{../../../template} resolves correctly with -I.
CmdLine
{
    -n15 -n16 -I
}
